Package: lua-smpltmpl
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Provides: ${lua:Provides}
XB-Lua-Versions: ${lua:Versions}
Description: simple Lua HTML templating system
 Lua-smpltmpl supports a simple templating language intended for
 creating HTML output. Lua expressions and templates can be
 inserted.
 .
 The latest source code and documentation is always available from the
 module's website: <https://geoffrichards.co.uk/lua/smpltmpl/>

Package: lua-smpltmpl-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Depends: lua-smpltmpl (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Provides: ${lua:Provides}
XB-Lua-Versions: ${lua:Versions}
Description: documentation for the Lua SmplTmpl module
 This package contains documentation for the liblua5.3-smpltmpl package,
 in the lua-smpltmpl(3) man page.  This describes the complete API of the
 Lua module.  A more attractive version of the same thing is available on
 the module's website: <https://geoffrichards.co.uk/lua/smpltmpl/doc/>
